@startuml
!define RECTANGLE class

participant "SparX Service\n(Krikkit/Eccentrica)" as Service
participant "wonko-client" as Client
participant "Kafka" as Kafka
participant "wonko/core" as Core
participant "wonko/kafka/consume" as Consumer
participant "wonko/kafka/produce" as Producer
participant "wonko/alert" as Alert
participant "wonko/export/prometheus/create" as PrometheusCreate
participant "wonko/export/prometheus/register" as PrometheusRegister
participant "wonko/web_server" as WebServer
participant "Prometheus" as Prometheus
participant "PagerDuty API" as PagerDuty

== Initialization ==
Core -> Core: Start Nrepl server
Core -> Consumer: Start consumption processes
Core -> WebServer: Start web server
WebServer -> WebServer: Setup routes for metrics endpoint

== Event Monitoring Flow ==
Service -> Client: Send event/metric
Client -> Kafka: Publish event to topic
Kafka -> Consumer: Consume event from topic
Consumer -> Consumer: Process event
Consumer -> PrometheusCreate: Create metric from event
PrometheusCreate -> PrometheusRegister: Register metric
PrometheusRegister -> PrometheusRegister: Store metric in registry

== Alert Processing Flow ==
Consumer -> Alert: Check event against alert criteria
Alert -> Alert: Evaluate alert conditions
alt Alert triggered
    Alert -> Alert: Queue alert to thread pool
    activate Alert
    Alert -> PagerDuty: Send notification via HTTP
    PagerDuty --> Alert: Acknowledge notification
    deactivate Alert
    Alert -> Producer: Publish alert to Kafka
    Producer -> Kafka: Write alert message
end

== Metrics Exposition Flow ==
Prometheus -> WebServer: Scrape metrics endpoint (HTTP GET)
WebServer -> PrometheusRegister: Retrieve registered metrics
PrometheusRegister --> WebServer: Return metrics data
WebServer -> WebServer: Format metrics (TextFormat)
WebServer --> Prometheus: Return Prometheus-compatible metrics

== Data Clearing Flow ==
Prometheus -> WebServer: Request data clear (HTTP)
WebServer -> PrometheusRegister: Clear metrics registry
PrometheusRegister --> WebServer: Confirm cleared
WebServer --> Prometheus: Return success response

@enduml
